002package com.commercetools.api.models;
003
004/**
005 * Interface of a resource with an ID and version
006 * @param <T>
007 */
008public interface DomainResource<T extends DomainResource<T>> extends Identifiable<T> {
009    public String getId();
010
011    public Long getVersion();
012
013    default T get() {
014        return (T) this;
015    }
016}
